# Normalize all text to LF in the repo and working tree. The C toolchain, shell
# scripts, and Docker build are all Linux-consumed — CRLF would break the container
# entrypoint (bench-driver.sh) and is undesirable everywhere else here.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Be explicit for the Linux-executed files:
*.sh         text eol=lf
*.c          text eol=lf
*.Dockerfile text eol=lf
Dockerfile   text eol=lf
